&lt;Ventra Management Inc> said ithas formed a joint venture that it will manage to provide leasefinancing for &lt;Modular Computer Systems Inc>    Ventra said it will fund leases with the proceeds of a 60mln dlr leasing equipment receivable bond offering underwrittenby Mabon, Nugent and Co.  It said the venture has alreadygenerated about 10 mln dlrs in computer leases. Reuter&#3;